@startuml Decorator_Pattern_Sequence_Diagram

participant "GameController" as Controller
participant "Bomberman" as Bomberman
participant "BombermanAdapter" as Adapter
participant "SpeedBoostDecorator" as SpeedDec
participant "BombCountBoostDecorator" as CountDec
participant "BombPowerBoostDecorator" as PowerDec

Controller -> Bomberman: create Bomberman()
activate Bomberman
Bomberman --> Controller: bomberman instance
deactivate Bomberman

Controller -> Adapter: BombermanAdapter(bomberman)
activate Adapter
Adapter --> Controller: adapter instance
deactivate Adapter

Controller -> SpeedDec: SpeedBoostDecorator(adapter)
activate SpeedDec
SpeedDec --> Controller: speed_decorator
deactivate SpeedDec

Controller -> CountDec: BombCountBoostDecorator(speed_decorator)
activate CountDec
CountDec --> Controller: count_decorator
deactivate CountDec

Controller -> PowerDec: BombPowerBoostDecorator(count_decorator)
activate PowerDec
PowerDec --> Controller: final_decorator
deactivate PowerDec

Controller -> PowerDec: get_speed()
activate PowerDec
PowerDec -> CountDec: get_speed()
activate CountDec
CountDec -> SpeedDec: get_speed()
activate SpeedDec
SpeedDec -> Adapter: get_speed()
activate Adapter
Adapter -> Bomberman: speed
activate Bomberman
Bomberman --> Adapter: 1.0
deactivate Bomberman
Adapter --> SpeedDec: 1.0
deactivate Adapter
SpeedDec -> SpeedDec: multiply by 1.25
SpeedDec --> CountDec: 1.25
deactivate SpeedDec
CountDec --> PowerDec: 1.25
deactivate CountDec
PowerDec --> Controller: 1.25
deactivate PowerDec

note right of Adapter
    **Adapter Pattern**
    Bomberman'ı PlayerInterface'e
    adapte eder
end note

note right of SpeedDec
    **Decorator Pattern**
    Runtime'da özellik ekler
    Chain of decorators
end note

@enduml

